definitions.definition: An edible clam with a hard shell found along the Atlantic Coast of North America, from species Mercenaria mercenaria , formerly Venus mercenaria .

subdefinitions.definition: The largest size of such an edible clam, generally considered only fit for use in chowders and other clam dishes.

definitions.definition: A similar edible clam, of species Arctica islandica , found along coasts around the North Atlantic, generally in deeper waters.
